  <h2>Support</h2>
  <p>
    <code>funcgo</code> provides the standard development and build commands for
    <code>func</code> projects. The full workflow is documented in
    <a href="/tooling">Tooling</a>.
  </p>
  <div class="overflow-x-auto">
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Signature</th>
